cast.overview: The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.
cast.title: Interstellar

details.biography: Lena Georgas is an American stage, film and television actress and photographer. She holds a BA in Drama from Vassar College, Poughkeepsie, New York, USA, and also studied Theater at the British American Drama Academy, London, England, UK.
details.name: Lena Georgas
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
